General Info
 - PasswdManager a command-line interactive python script to create & manage password.
 - PasswdManager heavily depends on Py3K (written as) and PyCrypto (AES encryption, SHA265 digest, random number) while slightly depends on XSel (to communicate with X's clipboard), so make sure you have first two installed before download and run this script.
   - Py3K: http://www.python.org/getit/releases/3.0/
   - PyCrypto: https://www.dlitz.net/software/pycrypto/
   - XSel: http://www.kfish.org/software/xsel/
 - I just insert encrypted password infomation (cypertext) at the end of the script, so we can save the trouble of managing two closely coupled files everywhere.
 

