= Help ===============================================================

 >> ?
List of possible commands:

l       Show logs
n       Creat new entry
q       Exit this script
0       Operate on entry 'github'
u       Update main passwd
ex      Export unencryted password info in base64
d0      Remove entry 'github'
?       Print this


Entries (main password updated 0:02:03 ago):
0       github  username        0:01:28

 >> 
======================================================================

= Create a entry =====================================================

Entries (main password updated 0:00:00 ago):

 >> n
Creat a new entry, directly hit Enter to cancel
Input entry name >> github
Input username >> username
Input passphrase >> aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaabbbbbbbbbbbb
Input password length (default 15, min 3, max 127) >> 
New entry github created

Entries (main password updated 0:00:35 ago):
0       github  username        0:00:00

